item.title: Write the Docs Podcast
item.description: I chatted with the Write the Docs podcast team about: The Write the Docs Australian conference more wind-downs and ramp-ups, Highlights from the just-finished WTD Prague conference, Speakers announced for upcoming Write the Docs Australia conference, The Good Docs Project, The tech writing scene in Australia
